[Kuraa-ma] So much fun!

00:23:27.941 --> 00:23:28.942
So much fun!

00:23:28.976 --> 00:23:30.644
Kuraa-ma's having fun!

00:23:30.677 --> 00:23:32.913
Yes, there, there, Kuraa-ma!

00:23:32.946 --> 00:23:34.882
Oh, you're just so
incredibly cute!

00:23:34.915 --> 00:23:36.550
[Kuraa-ma] Pet me again!

00:23:36.583 --> 00:23:37.551
It's so much fun!

00:23:37.584 --> 00:23:38.719
Yes, you are!

00:23:38.752 --> 00:23:40.988
[Kuraa-ma] So much fun!

00:23:41.889 --> 00:23:44.191
[Sumire] (gasping)
Oh, the sound's so-

00:23:44.224 --> 00:23:46.293
[Wasabi] Namida's
jutsu's so powerful,

00:23:46.326 --> 00:23:47.794
I think I'm losing my hearing!

00:23:47.828 --> 00:23:49.062
[Namida] I've made my decision!

00:23:49.096 --> 00:23:51.532
For everyone's sake,
I won't cry anymore!

00:23:51.565 --> 00:23:54.301
I'm going to start training
with a new jutsu instead!

00:23:54.334 --> 00:23:55.369
[Hanabi] Oh!

00:23:55.402 --> 00:23:57.504
It's rare that we see you
so determined, Namida!

00:23:57.538 --> 00:23:59.907
All right, time to
train extra hard!

00:23:59.940 --> 00:24:01.175
(Namida shrieking)

00:24:01.208 --> 00:24:03.911
Next time on "Boruto:
Naruto Next Generations",

00:24:03.944 --> 00:24:06.213
"Blood, Sweat, and Namida."

00:24:06.246 --> 00:24:08.081
[Sumire] You know,
Hanabi Sensei,

00:24:08.115 --> 00:24:10.417
